C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FRob_ThaBuilder%2Fstatus%2F1823147959803957619%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escreenshots%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20satirical%20social%20media%20posts%20as%20if%20they're%20fact%2C%20like%20one%20from%20the%20parody%20Facebook%20meme%20page%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fthesportsmemery%2Fphotos%2Faustralian-olympic-break-dancer-rachael-gunn-proudly-declares-she-achieved-exact%2F1007296881372194%2F%3Fpaipv%3D0%26eav%3DAfaC71jXnVznZf0UgcPfheQgyMQMaZ90PyFJsOw_aR3aVXnPk38g4EPQ927jryQ2c1s%26_rdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Sports%20Memery%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20depicts%20Raygun%20saying%20that%20she%20trained%20for%20%26quot%3Bexactly%2037%20minutes%26quot%3B%20before%20competing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Change.org%20petition%2C%20which%20has%20since%20been%20taken%20down%2C%20served%20as%20a%20vehicle%20for%20its%20claims%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fkarriehiggins%2Fstatus%2F1823405871449461090%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espread%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FDD_Geopolitics%2Fstatus%2F1823606930977513591%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmaplefrosteds%2Fstatus%2F1823351264412942657%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leading%20the%20AOC%20to%20demand%20its%20removal%20in%20the%20statement%20linked%20above.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20a%20Change.org%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20email%20statement%20that%20after%20being%20flagged%20for%20misinformation%2C%20the%20petition%20had%20been%20reviewed%20against%20the%20platform's%20community%20guidelines%20and%20eventually%20removed.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20that%20point%2C%20it%20had%20reached%20over%2056%2C000%20signatures%2C%20per%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.ph%2FTLtru%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earchived%20snapshot%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22200