lopment%20spooked%20investors%2C%20at%20least%20temporarily%2C%20who%20are%20now%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20what%20the%20jobs%20market%20does%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Jon%20Wolfenbarger%2C%20the%20recession%20indication%20from%20the%20Sahm%20Rule%20came%20as%20no%20surprise.%20The%20Portugal-based%20founder%20of%20investing%20newsletter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FBullAndBearProfits.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBullAndBearProfits.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20warning%20of%20a%20downturn%20for%20some%20time%20now%20amid%20worrying%20signals%20like%20an%20inverted%20Treasury%20yield%20curve%2C%20another%20recession%20indicator%20with%20a%20perfect%20track%20record%20going%20back%20several%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Sahm%20Rule%20isn't%20the%20only%20labor%20market%20indicator%20that%20should%20be%20worrying%20investors%2C%20Wolfenbarger%20said%20in%20an%20August%205%20note.%20Others%20show%20alarming%20trends%20as%20well%2C%20according%20to%20the%20former%20JPMorgan%20and%20Merrill%20Lynch%20investment%20banker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20Sahm%20Rule%20in%20concept%2C%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20has%20risen%20by%200.9%25%20from%20recent%20lows%20of%203.4%25%2C%20crossing%20the%20two-year%20moving%20average.%20Historically%2C%20that%20has%20meant%20a%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22unemployment%20rate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bfc0b75da406397bf6b86a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221302%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBullAndBearProfits.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20employment%20growth%2C%20or%20the%20rate%20of%20change%20in%20the%20number%20of%20employed%20people%20year-over-year.%20It's%20now%20at%200%25%2C%20and%20most%20times%20when%20it%20has%20dipped%20negative%2C%20it%20has%20meant%20a%20recession%2C%20Wolfenbarger%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222156%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22employment%20level%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bfc0dcb4912df3ae1c780b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22902%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBullAndBearProfits.com%2FSt.%20Louis%20Fed%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20weekly%20hours%20worked%20have%20also%20dropped%20to%20around%2034.2.%20If%20that%20number%20falls%20further%2C%20it%20would%20be%20the%20third%20time%20in%20the%20last%2020%20years.%20The%20only%20other%20instances%20were%20the%202008%20and%202020%20recessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222158%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22average%20weekly%20hours%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bfc177b4912df3ae1c783f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22866%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBullAndBearProfits.com%2FSt.%20Louis%20Fed%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20according%20to%20ISM%20data%2C%20manufacturing%20employment%20is%20declining%2C%20which%20tends%20to%20track%20closely%20with%20overall%20employment.%20This%20could%20mean%20the%20surge%20in%20unemployment%20has%20more%20room%20to%20run%2C%20Wolfenbarger%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222222%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ism%20employment%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bfc134b4912df3ae1c7831%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBullAndBearProfits.com%2FTrahan%20Macro%20Research%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recession%20would%20mean%20big%20trouble%20for%20investors%20given%20how%20high%20stock%20valuations%20are%2C%20Wolfenbarger%20said%20in%20a%20call%20with%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Friday.%20He%20cited%20John%20Hussman's%20total%20market%20cap%20of%20nonfinancial%20stocks-to-gross%20value%20added%20valuation%20ratio%2C%20which%20hit%20all-time%20highs%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20measure%20to%20return%20to%20levels%20where%20investors%20can%20expect%20long-term%20annualized%20returns%20of%2010%25%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20would%20have%20to%20fall%20about%2070%25%20from%20current%20levels%2C%20Wolfenbarger%20said.%20Losses%20of%20at%20least%2050%25%20consistent%20with%20Hussman's%20measure%20also%20happened%20following%20the%201929%2C%202000%2C%20and%202008%20crashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221822%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hussman%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20potential%20losses%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bfc0ff1aa2ac29ee3207cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221062%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHussman%20Funds%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22191a7445-f3e7-4f43-9c04-57ec05e00a29%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWolfenbarger's%20views%20in%20context%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Wolfenbarger's%20outlook%20on%20stocks%20is%20well%20outside%20Wall%20Street%20consensus%2C%20his%20views%20on%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20US%20economy%20have%20moved%20more%20into%20the%20mainstream%20range%20of%20possible%20outcomes%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20will%20have%20their%20eyes%20on%20August's%20jobs%20and%20unemployment%20reports%20early%20next%20month%20%E2%80%94%20if%20the%20numbers%20are%20downbeat%2C%20the%20market%20could%20enter%20another%20selling%20period%20as%20it%20did%20in%20the%20days%20after%20July's%20jobs%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20signs%20for%20optimism%20that%20the%20US%20economy%20can%20avoid%20a%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20argue%20that%20July's%20jobs%20data%20was%20impacted%20by%20Hurricane%20Beryl%20in%20Louisiana%20and%20Texas.%20Labor%20participation%20is%20also%20picking%20up%2C%20which%20has%20helped%20fuel%20the%20rise%20in%20unemployment%20and%20is%20why%20Sahm%20thinks%20her%20indicator%20is%20producing%20a%20false%20positive.%20Inflation%20also%20fell%20below%203%25%20year-over-year%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%202021%2C%20giving%20the%20Fed%20added%20confidence%20to%20cut%20interest%20rates%20at%20its%20September%20meeting%2C%20which%20would%20aim%20to%20start%20providing%20a%20boost%20to%20demand%20in%20the%20economy%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20a%20bit%20too%20early%20to%20tell.%20For%20the%20time%20being%2C%20investors%20have%20seemingly%20put%20their%20fears%20aside%20for%20now%2C%20with%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20inching%20back%20toward%20all-time%20highs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20labor%20market%20does%20continue%20to%20deteriorate%2C%20however%2C%20Wolfenbarger's%20stock%20market%20outlook%20%E2%80%94%20just%20like%20his%20warnings%20about%20the%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20could%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20start%20to%20look%20more%20plausible%20in%20the%20months%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-recession-signals-sp500-outlook-unemployment-rate-wolfenbarger-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723885201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658b2cda1c5c7b8c9a0c1579%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-recession-signals-sp500-outlook-unemployment-rate-wolfenbarger-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20addition%20to%20the%20Sahm%20Rule%2C%20other%20labor%20market%20indicators%20show%20concerning%20trends%20as%20well.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-recession-signals-sp500-outlook-unemployment-rate-wolfenbarger-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20CCTV%2C%20Stray%20Dog%20Goes%20On%20Biting%20Spree%20In%20UP%2C%20Attacks%2017%20People%20In%201%20Hour%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20rabid%20dog%20went%20on%20a%20biting%20spree%20in%20UP's%20Gorakhpur%2C%20attacking%2017%20people%20including%20children%20and%20women%20within%20an%20hour%20on%20August%2014.%20CCTV%20video%20captured%20the%20dog%20viciously%20attacking%20a%2022-year-old%20student%20as%20he%20talked%20on%20his%20phone%20outside%20his%20house%20in%20Gorakhpur's%20Shahpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20from%20a%20CCTV%20camera%20outside%20Ashish%20Yadav's%20home%20in%20the%20Awas%20Vikas%20Colony%20shows%20the%20BBA%20student%20walking%20in%20front%20of%20his%20house%20as%20he%20talked%20on%20the%20phone%20at%209.45%20pm%20on%20Wednesday.%20Suddenly%2C%20a%20stray%20dog%20rushes%20towards%20him%20baring%20his%20teeth%20and%20begins%20attacking%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshish%20tries%20to%20back%20off%20and%20kick%20the%20dog%20but%20it%20does%20not%20stop%20barking%20and%20biting.%20It%20sinks%20its%20teeth%20into%20his%20leg%20as%20Ashish%20falls%20to%20the%20ground.%20The%20dog%20then%20jumps%20and%20bites%20him%20in%20the%20face%20before%20running%20away.%20The%20video%20shows%20him%20bleeding%20from%20the%20mouth%2C%20eyes%20and%20lips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%2C%20the%20dog%20made%20a%20woman%2C%20who%20was%20returning%20home%20and%20standing%20at%20the%20gate%20of%20her%20house%2C%20its%20prey.%20Attacking%20her%20on%20the%20knee%20and%20leg%2C%20the%20dog%20scurried%20away%2C%20she%20said.%20The%20deep%20wound%20on%20her%20knee%20required%20several%20stitches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20the%20dog%20attacked%20two%20girls%20who%20were%20playing%20outside%20their%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshish's%20father%20Vijay%20Yadav%20said%20that%20when%20he%20took%20him%20to%20the%20district%20hospital%20for%20a%20rabies%20vaccine%2C%20he%20was%20told%20the%20hospital%20had%20run%20out%20of%20the%20shot.%20The%20victims%20say%20they%20have%20informed%20the%20municipal%20corporation%20about%20the%20dog%20attacks%20but