0healthcare%20workers%20in%20their%20respective%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20of%20all%20stakeholders%20including%20the%20State%20Governments%20will%20be%20invited%20to%20share%20their%20suggestions%20with%20the%20Committee%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20also%20requested%20the%20agitating%20doctors%20to%20resume%20their%20duties%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Blarger%20public%20interest%26quot%3B%20and%20in%20view%20of%20the%20rising%20cases%20of%20dengue%20and%20malaria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E5%20Demands%20Of%20Doctors%20On%20Nationwide%20Strike%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMA%20has%20put%20forth%20the%20following%20five%20demands%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20wants%20a%20significant%20policy%20to%20address%20violence%20against%20doctors%20and%20hospitals.%20The%20doctors'%20body%20is%20pushing%20for%20a%20Central%20Act%20that%20would%20incorporate%20the%20amendments%20made%20in%202023%20to%20the%20Epidemic%20Diseases%20Act%20of%201897%20into%20the%20proposed%20Hospital%20Protection%20Bill%20of%202019.%20This%20move%2C%20it%20said%2C%20would%20strengthen%20the%20existing%20legislation%20in%2025%20states.%20The%20IMA%20has%20suggested%20that%20an%20ordinance%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20enacted%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20would%20be%20appropriate%20in%20this%20situation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20IMA%20has%20also%20demanded%20that%20hospitals%20be%20declared%20safe%20zones%20with%20the%20first%20step%20being%20mandatory%20security%20entitlements.%20%26quot%3BThe%20security%20protocols%20of%20all%20hospitals%20should%20be%20no%20less%20than%20(that%20of)%20an%20airport.%20Declaring%20the%20hospitals%20as%20safe%20zones%20with%20mandatory%20security%20entitlements%20is%20the%20first%20step.%20CCTVs%2C%20deployment%20of%20security%20personnel%2C%20and%20the%20protocols%20can%20follow%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20IMA%20has%20demanded%20a%20thorough%20overhaul%20of%20the%20working%20and%20living%20conditions%20of%20resident%20doctors%2C%20including%20the%2036-hour%20duty%20shift%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20in%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20safe%20spaces%20to%20take%20a%20rest.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20IMA%20has%20also%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bmeticulous%20and%20professional%26quot%3B%20investigation%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20horror%20in%20a%20specific%20time%20frame%20and%20rendering%20of%20justice%20besides%20identifying%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20vandalism%20of%20the%20hospital%20premises%20and%20awarding%20exemplary%20punishment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20doctors'%20body%20has%20also%20sought%20an%20appropriate%20and%20dignified%20compensation%20to%20the%20bereaved%20family%20commensurate%20with%20the%20cruelty%20inflicted.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723884420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fk2d8bgqg_doctors-strike_625x300_17_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-set-up-committee-for-safety-of-doctors-amid-nationwide-protests-6356885%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Doctors%20have%20called%20a%2024-hour%20nationwide%20strike%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20junior%20doctor%20in%20Kolkata.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Thank%20you%20for%20...'%3A%20What%20Kamala%20Harris%20said%20about%20Meghan%20Markle%20as%20rumors%20swirl%20of%20Duchess'%20possible%202024%20endorsement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723884244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112586269%2Cimgsize-113312.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-elections-kamala-harris-said-about-meghan-markle-as-rumors-swirl-of-duchess-possible-2024-endo