20a%20century%2C%20the%20attempts%20at%20Cuba's%20most%20iconic%20leader%20involved%20spies%2C%20Mafia%20hitmen%2C%20James%20Bond-style%20death%20devices%2C%20and%20other%20methods%20that%20may%20seem%20like%20something%20out%20of%20an%20Ian%20Fleming%20novel.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNow%2C%20a%20new%20docuseries%2C%20Mafia%20Spies%2C%20streaming%20on%20Paramount%2B%2C%20exposed%20the%20actual%20how%20the%20CIA%20cooperated%20with%20the%20mafia%20to%20organise%20Castro's%20assassination.%20It's%20based%20on%20a%20book%2C%20authored%20by%20Thomas%20Maier%2C%20of%20the%20same%20name.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20intricate%20storylines%20and%20large%20ensemble%20of%20politicians%2C%20mobsters%2C%20spies%2C%20revolutionaries%2C%20and%20entertainers%20feature%20in%20the%20six%20episodes%20of%20Mafia%20Spies.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnCastro%20was%20the%20newly%20appointed%20prime%20minister%20of%20Cuba%2C%20and%20the%20CIA%2C%20then%20headed%20by%20Allen%20Dulles%2C%20intended%20to%20topple%20him.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTo%20assassinate%20Castro%2C%20the%20CIA%20recruited%20organised%20criminal%20figures%2C%20Sam%20Giancana%20and%20John%20Roselli%20of%20the%20Chicago%20Outfit%2C%20through%20a%20middleman%20named%20Robert%20Maheu%2C%20who%20was%20an%20attorney%20and%20businessman.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNotably%2C%20the%20mafia%20had%20their%20own%20motivations%20for%20wanting%20Castro%20gone%20as%20Havana's%20casinos%20ceased%20to%20be%20a%20cash%20cow%20sanctuary%20for%20them%20when%20he%20took%20over%20in%201959.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20series%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20unsuccessful%201961%20Bay%20of%20Pigs%20invasion%20of%20Cuba%2C%20the%201962%20Cuban%20Missile%20Crisis%20and%20the%201963%20assassination%20of%20US%20President%20John%20F.%20Kennedy.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20accomplish%20its%20aim%2C%20the%20CIA%20and%20its%20mafia%20allies%20used%20everything%20from%20poison%20tablets%20to%20a%20deadly%20%26quot%3Bhoney%20pot%26quot%3B%20that%20involved%20enlisting%20a%20woman%20to%20murder%20and%20seduce.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMaier's%20book%20is%20based%20in%20large%20part%20on%20documents%20on%20Kennedy's%20assassination%20that%20the%20National%20Archives%20published%20in%20batches%20in%202017%20and%202018.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20JFK%20records%20demonstrate%20that%20despite%20their%20deadly%20reputation%2C%20Giancana%20and%20Roselli%2C%20the%20Mafia%20duo%2C%20were%20unable%20to%20assassinate%20Castro.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20potential%20assassin%20in%20Havana%20was%20handed%20poison%20tablets%20by%20the%20CIA.%20However%2C%20he%20got%20cold%20feet%20before%20tampering%20with%20Castro's%20food.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Church%20Committee%2C%20a%20Senate%20committee%20that%20documented%20abuses%20by%20intelligence%20services%20in%20the%20mid-1970s%2C%20claims%20that%20the%20cigar%20plot%2C%20perhaps%20the%20most%20well-known%20attempt%20on%20Castro's%20life%2C%20began%20in%201960.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20the%20Committee's%20investigation%2C%20an%20official%20was%20handed%20a%20box%20of%20Castro's%20favourite%20cigars%20along%20with%20orders%20to%20inject%20them%20with%20deadly%20poison.%20The%20cigars%20were%20tainted%20with%20a%20botulinum%20toxin%20so%20strong%20that%20ingesting%20one%20would%20result%20in%20death.%20It%20is%20unclear%20from%20the%20record%20if%20there%20was%20an%20effort%20to%20give%20Castro%20the%20cigars.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnCastro%20loved%20scuba%20diving%2C%20so%20it%20should%20come%20as%20no%20surprise%20that%20the%20CIA%20investigated%20the%20potential%20of%20creating%20an%20explosive%20seashell%20to%20assassinate%20him%20during%20one%20of%20his%20outings.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20the%20Church%20Committee%20report%2C%20in%201963%2C%20Desmond%20Fitzgerald%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20%5Banti-Castro%20CIA%5D%20Task%20Force%2C%20ordered%20his%20assistant%20to%20find%20out%20whether%20it%20would%20be%20possible%20to%20place%20a%20seashell%20that%20could%20be%20set%20to%20detonate%20in%20a%20place%20where%20Castro%20frequently%20went%20diving.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnOther%20unsuccessful%20Florida-based%20commando%20operations%20were%20attributed%20to%20misfortune%20or%20inauspicious%20timing.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFighters%20with%20CIA%20training%20who%20were%20discovered%20invading%20Cuban%20coastlines%20during%20nighttime%20assaults%20were%20frequently%20imprisoned%20and%20occasionally%20put%20to%20death%20by%20firing%20squad.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20JFK%20documents%20also%20show%20how%20Castro's%20own%20network%20of%20double%20agents%20and%20supporters%20in%20Florida%20thwarted%20CIA%20operations%20and%20assisted%20in%20protecting%20the%20communist%20leader.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20few%20of%20the%20conspirators%20who%20were%20associated%20with%20the%20two%20gangsters%20betrayed%20them%20for%20personal%20gain.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723882020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-12%2Ffidel-castro_650x400_71480827717.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrom-poison-tablets-to-cigars-how-the-us-tried-and-failed-to-kill-fidel-castro-6356579%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20JFK%20documents%20also%20show%20how%20Castro's%20own%20network%20of%20double%20agents%20and%20supporters%20in%20Florida%20thwarted%20CIA%20operations%20and%20assisted%20in%20protecting%20the%20communist%20leader.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian-Origin%20man%20shot%20dead%20by%20teenager%20in%20convenience%20store%20robbery%20in%20North%20Carolina%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723881799000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112585541%2Cimgsize-6534.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2