expressed%20interest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20What%20Is%20MUDA%20Row%20In%20Which%20Siddaramaiah%20Will%20Be%20Prosecuted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20faces%20a%20big%20challenge%20as%20the%20Governor%20has%20sanctioned%20his%20prosecution%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20site%20allotment%20by%20the%20Mysuru%20Urban%20Development%20Authority%20(MUDA).%20The%20BJP%20has%20been%20campaigning%20against%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20his%20government%20over%20the%20alleged%20land%20scam%20and%20demanding%20his%20resignation.%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20denied%20all%20charges%20against%20him%20and%20his%20wife%20BM%20Parvathi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20The%20Row%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MUDA%20land%20scam%20row%20pertains%20to%20the%20allotment%20of%20compensatory%20land%20parcels%20to%20Siddaramaiah's%20wife%20when%20he%20was%20the%20chief%20minister.%20Social%20activists%20allege%20irregularities%20in%20the%20process%20that%20allegedly%20caused%20loss%20worth%20crores%20to%20the%20state%20exchequer.%20Top%20officials%20in%20the%20MUDA%20and%20revenue%20department%20are%20also%20named%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20three%20activists%20-Pradeep%20Kumar%2C%20TJ%20Abraham%2C%20and%20Snehamayi%20Krishna%20-%20had%20requested%20Governor%20Thaawarchand%20Gehlot%20for%20action%20against%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abraham%2C%20an%20anti-corruption%20activist%2C%20had%20alleged%20the%20multi-crore%20scam%20caused%20huge%20losses%20to%20the%20state%20exchequer%20in%20his%20petition%20to%20the%20Governor%20and%20requested%20him%20to%20sanction%20his%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-chief-minister-siddaramaiah-to-be-prosecuted-in-land-scam-case-6355735%5C%22%3EKarnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20To%20Be%20Prosecuted%20In%20Land%20Scam%20Case%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20he%20had%20complained%20to%20the%20Lokayukta%20police%20that%20the%20allotment%20of%2014%20sites%20in%20an%20upscale%20Mysuru%20neighbourhood%20to%20Siddaramaiah's%20wife%20BM%20Parvathi%20was%20illegal.%20This%20caused%20a%20Rs%2045%20crore%20loss%2C%20he%20had%20claimed.%20Besides%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20the%20complaint%20also%20named%20his%20wife%2C%20son%20S%20Yathindra%2C%20and%20senior%20MUDA%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20activist%2C%20Snehamayi%20Krishna%20also%20alleged%20the%20involvement%20of%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20and%20MUDA%20and%20administrative%20officials%20in%20the%20alleged%20land%20scam.%20A%20fresh%20FIR%20was%20not%20filed%20as%20the%20police%20said%20probe%20was%20already%20underway%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESiddaramaiah's%20Defence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramiah%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20land%20for%20which%20his%20wife%20received%20compensation%2C%20was%20gifted%20by%20her%20brother%20Mallikarjuna%20in%201998.%20But%20activist%20Krishna%20alleged%20that%20Mallikarjuna%20had%20procured%20it%20illegally%20in%202004%20and%20got%20it%20registered%20it%20using%20forged%20documents%20with%20the%20help%20of%20government%20and%20revenue%20officials.%20The%20land%20was%20shown%20to%20have%20been%20bought%20in%201998.%20Ms%20Parvathi%20sought%20compensation%20for%20this%20land%20in%202014%2C%20when%20Siddaramaiah%20was%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20had%20denied%20the%20charges%20as%20%26quot%3Bpolitically%20motivated%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20his%20wife%20was%20awarded%20compensation%20when%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20power%20and%20that%20it%20was%20her%20right.%20%26quot%3BThey%20(BJP)%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20gave%20the%20site%2C%20now%20if%20they%20call%20it%20illegal%2C%20how%20should%20one%20respond%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAction%20In%20MUDA%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20Thaawarchand%20Gehlot%20has%20sanctioned%20the%20Lokayukta%20to%20prosecute%20Siddaramaiah%20based%20on%20petitions%20by%20the%20three%20activists.%20The%20Karnataka%20BJP%20welcomed%20the%20Governor's%20go-ahead%20while%20the%20Congress%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitically%20motivated%20conspiracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20Governor%20had%20issued%20a%20%26quot%3Bshow-cause%20notice%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20reply%20within%20seven%20days%20why%20he%20shouldn't%20be%20prosecuted.%20The%20Karnataka%20government%20had%20advised%20the%20Governor%20to%20withdraw%20the%20notice%20and%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bgross%20misuse%20of%20the%20Constitutional%20Office%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723880160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Facnhg56_siddaramaiah-pti_625x300_17_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fexplained-what-is-muda-row-in-which-siddaramaiah-will-be-prosecuted-6356612%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20faces%20a%20big%20challenge%20as%20the%20Governor%20has%20sanctioned%20his%20prosecution%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20site%20allotment%20by%20the%20Mysuru%20Urban%20Development%20Authority%20(MUDA).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vinesh's%20First%20Statement%20After%20Returning%20To%20India%20Post%20Olympics%20Heartbreak%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWrestler%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20who%20arrived%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20to%20a%20rousing%20reception%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Airport%20on%20Saturday%20said%20that%20she%20is%20%26quot%3Bgrateful%26quot%3B%20for%20receiving%20such%20love%20and%20respect%20from%20people.%20Vinesh%20was%20accompanied%20by%20Bajrang%20Punia%2C%20Sakshi%20Malik%20and%20Congress%20MP%20Deepender%20Singh%20Hooda%20for%20a%20roadshow%20after%20her%20arrival%20in%20Delhi%20today.%20Speaking%20to%20ANI%2C%20Vinesh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20grateful%20for%20this%20love%20and%20respect%20I%20have%20received%20from%20my%20countrymen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBajrang%20Punia%20said%20that%20Vinesh%20has%20been%20welcomed%20like%20a%20champion.%20He%20also%20thanked%20people%20for%20showing%20support.%20%26quot%3BShe%20(Vinesh%20Phogat)%20is%20being%20welcomed%20like%20a%20champion.%20The%20country%20saw%20Vinesh's%20journey%20from%20the%20streets%20to%20the%20podium.%20We%20thank%20all%20the%20countrymen%2C%26quot%3B%20Bajrang%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESakshi%20Malik%20said%20that%20Vinesh%20has%20done%20a%20lot%20for%20the%20women%20and%20the%20nation%20and%20hoped%20that%20people%20would%20continue%20to%20respect%20Vinesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20is%20a%20big%20day.%20What%20Vinesh%20has%20done%20for%20all%20the%20women%20and%20the%20nation%20is%20commendable.%20I%20just%20hope%20the%20people%20will%20continue%20to%20respect%20her...%20for%20us%2C%20she%20is%20an%20Olympic%20champion%2C%26quot%3B%20Sakshi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana-born%20wrestler%20turned%20emotional%20and%20broke%20down%20into%20tears%20during%20the%20reception%20at%20the%20airport%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Paris%2C%20Vinesh%20had%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20make%20the%20final%20of%20an%20Olympics.%20She%20was%20however%2C%20disqualified%20from%20the%2050%20kg%20gold%20medal%20bout%20after%20she%20was%20found%20to%20be%20100%20gms%20overweight.%20On%20Wednesday%20the%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20for%20Sport%20(CAS)%20dismissed%20her%20petition%20to%20be%20awarded%20a%20joint%20silver.%20She%20announced%20her%20retirement%20from%20wrestling%20on%20August%208%2C%20a%20day%20after%20her%20disqualification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20crowd%20gathered%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Airport%20to%20welcome%20the%2029-year-old.%20Fans%20showered%20flower%20petals%20upon%20her%20arrival%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%208%2C%20Vinesh%20penned%20an%20emotional%20to%20announce%20her%20decision%20to%20retire%20from%20wrestling.%20%26quot%3BMaa%20kushti%20(wrestling)%20won%20against%20me%2C%20I%20lost.%20Forgive%20me%2C%20your%20dream%20and%20my%20courage%20have%20been%20broken.%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20more%20strength%20now.%20Goodbye%20Wrestling%202001-2024.%20I%20will%20always%20be%20indebted%20to%20you%20all%20for%20forgiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20Phogat%20said%20in%20her%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723880160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F88cv1es8_vinesh-phogat-_625x300_17_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwrestling%2Fvinesh-phogats-first-statement-after-returning-to-india-post-paris-olympics-heartbreak-6356576%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vinesh%20Phogat%20arrived%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20to%20a%20rousing%20reception%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Airport%20on%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%20ceasefire%20deal%20closer%20than%20ever%2C%20Biden%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723880038000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F02bb%2Flive%2Ff9bc59a0-5c34-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc5ydpwe520go%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ceasefire%20talks%20come%20in%20the%20context%20of%20concern%20that%20the%20Israel-Gaza%20war%20may%20engulf%20the%20entire%20region.%22%2C%22author%