%20Kumar%2C%20TJ%20Abraham%2C%20and%20Snehamayi%20Krishna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20directed%20by%20the%20Governor%2C%20I%20am%20enclosing%20herewith%20the%20copy%20of%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Competent%20Authority%20on%20the%20request%20of%20sanction%20for%20prosecution%20against%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20Shri%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20under%20Section%2017%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%2C%201988%20and%20Section%20218%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarika%20Suraksha%20Samhitha%2C%202023%20for%20the%20commission%20of%20the%20alleged%20offences%20mention%20in%20the%20petitions%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20letter%20from%20the%20Governor's%20Secretariat%20to%20the%20activists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsiddaramaiah-muda-big-charge-against-siddaramaiahs-wife-amid-mysuru-land-compensation-row-6072815%5C%22%3EBig%20Charge%20Against%20Siddaramaiah's%20Wife%20Amid%20Mysuru%20Land%20Compensation%20Row%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister's%20Office%20(CMO)%20has%20confirmed%20that%20it%20has%20received%20this%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20welcomed%20the%20Governor's%20go-ahead%20to%20prosecute%20Siddaramaiah.%20%26quot%3BBy%20keeping%20enough%20records%20and%20evidences%20against%20the%20corrupt%20scandals%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20and%20against%20the%20bias%20and%20corruption%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20relatives%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20demonstrated%20that%20there%20is%20no%20one%20to%20shake%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20state%20BJP%20chief%20BY%20Vijayendra%20in%20an%20online%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefending%20him%2C%20Karnataka%20Congress%20alleged%20the%20Governor%20has%20been%20delaying%20action%20in%20probes%20against%20former%20chief%20minister%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20and%20former%20Karnataka%20ministers%20Sasikala%20Jolle%20and%20Murugesh%20Nirani.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Governor%20acted%20with%20alarming%20speed%20only%20on%20a%20baseless%20private%20complaint%20against%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20politically%20motivated%20conspiracy%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Governor%20had%20last%20month%20issued%20a%20%26quot%3Bshow-cause%20notice%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20directing%20him%20to%20reply%20to%20the%20allegations%20against%20him%20within%20seven%20days%20and%20state%20why%20he%20shouldn't%20be%20prosecuted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20sparked%20a%20resolution%20by%20the%20state%20cabinet%20asking%20the%20Governor%20not%20to%20sanction%20the%20prosecution.%20The%20Siddaramaiah-led%20government%20had%20also%20advised%20him%20to%20withdraw%20the%20notice%20and%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bgross%20misuse%20of%20the%20Constitutional%20Office%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Governor's%20notice%20followed%20a%20petition%20by%20anti-corruption%20activist%20TJ%20Abraham%20to%20prosecute%20Siddaramaiah%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20MUDA.%20In%20his%20petition%2C%20he%20alleged%20the%20multi-crore%20scam%20caused%20huge%20losses%20to%20the%20state's%20exchequer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20complaint%20filed%20with%20the%20Lokayukta%20police%20in%20July%2C%20Mr%20Abraham%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20allotment%20of%2014%20alternative%20sites%20in%20an%20upscale%20Mysuru%20neighbourhood%20to%20Siddaramaiah's%20wife%20BM%20Parvathi%20was%20illegal%2C%20which%20caused%20the%20exchequer%20a%20Rs%2045%20crore%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-16-acres-of-land-originally-purchased-for-rs-1-in-1935-siddaramaiah-on-muda-land-case-6194576%5C%22%3E3.16%20Acres%20Of%20Land%20Originally%20Bought%20For%20%E2%82%B9%201%20In%201935%3A%20Siddaramaiah%20On%20Mysuru%20Land%20Scam%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20named%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20wis%20wife%2C%20son%20S%20Yathindra%2C%20and%20senior%20MUDA%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20activist%2C%20Snehamayi%20Krishna%20also%20alleged%20the%20involvement%20of%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20and%20MUDA%20and%20administrative%20officials%20in%20the%20alleged%20land%20scam.%20A%20fresh%20FIR%20was%20not%20filed%20as%20the%20police%20said%20probe%20was%20already%20underway%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramiah%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20land%20for%20which%20his%20wife%20received%20compensation%2C%20was%20gifted%20by%20her%20brother%20Mallikarjuna%20in%201998.%20But%20activist%20Krishna%20alleged%20that%20Mallikarjuna%20had%20procured%20it%20illegally%20in%202004%20and%20got%20it%20registered%20it%20using%20forged%20documents%20with%20the%20help%20of%20government%20and%20revenue%20officials.%20The%20land%20was%20shown%20to%20have%20been%20bought%20in%201998.%20Ms%20Parvathi%20sought%20compensation%20for%20this%20land%20in%202014%2C%20when%20Siddaramaiah%20was%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20demanding%20a%20CBI%20probe%20in%20the%20case%2C%20held%20a%20weeklong%20%3Cem%3Epadayatra%20%3C%2Fem%3Efrom%20Bengaluru%20to%20Mysuru%20earlier%20this%20month%20against%20the%20Congress%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20BJP%20offensive%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20had%20said%20his%20wife%20was%20awarded%20compensation%20when%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20power%20and%20that%20it%20was%20her%20right.%20%26quot%3BThey%20(BJP)%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20gave%20the%20site%2C%20now%20if%20they%20call%20it%20illegal%2C%20how%20should%20one%20respond%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723878060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fm9dajj3g_siddaramaiah_625x300_23_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-chief-minister-siddaramaiah-to-be-prosecuted-in-land-scam-case-6355735%22%2C%22sum