%3ECitius%2C%20Altus%2C%20Fortius%20-%20Communiter%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%C2%A0meaning%20%26quot%3BFaster%2C%20Higher%2C%20Stronger%20-%20Together%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Olympics%2C%20from%20their%20very%20beginning%20in%20776%20BC%2C%20were%20about%20celebrating%20the%20frontiers%20of%20the%20human%20spirit%20and%20potential.%20The%20top%20athletes%2C%20while%20being%20born%20with%20genetic%20features%20suitable%20for%20sports%2C%20still%20spend%20more%20hours%20training%20for%20peak%20performance%20to%20literally%20infuse%20intelligence%20in%20each%20fibre%20of%20their%20muscle%2C%20learning%20to%20harness%20those%20billions%20of%20neurons%20to%20fire%20precisely%2C%20to%20fully%20exploit%20their%20mind-body%20connection%2C%20to%20finally%20reach%20their%20highest%20human%20potential.%20Usain%20Bolt%2C%20the%20famous%20sprinter%2C%20had%20a%20resting%20heart%20rate%20of%20around%2033%20BPM%2C%20while%20Michael%20Phelps%2C%20who%20won%2023%20golds%2C%20had%20a%20resting%20heart%20rate%20of%20about%2038%20BPM.%20A%20normal%20heart%20rate%20typically%20is%20around%2060%20BPM.%20They%20both%20spent%20insane%20hours%20on%20the%20track%20and%20in%20the%20pool%2C%20starting%20as%20young%20as%20seven%20years%2C%20striving%20for%20a%20zone%20of%20higher%20mind.%20This%20zone%20was%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20flow%26quot%3B%20by%20famous%20psychologist%20Mohali%20Csikszentmihalyi%20in%201970%2C%20as%20it%20melds%20together%20action%20and%20consciousness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeveloping%20Complex%20Human%20Intelligence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGames%20are%20a%20crucial%20element%20in%20exploring%20and%20growing%20multiple%20dimensions%20of%20complex%20human%20intelligence%20in%20young%20kids.%20The%20unstructured%20and%20playful%20nature%20of%20games%20allows%20for%20exploring%20the%20innate%20intelligence%20that%20the%20human%20body%20represents%2C%20demonstrating%20unique%20learning%20opportunities%20for%20the%20brain.%20Famous%20learning%20researcher%20Hilary%20Takeuchi%20took%20fMRI%20scans%20of%20brains%2C%20showing%20how%20creativity%20is%20related%20to%20brain%20activation%20via%20joyful%20experiences%20in%20play.%20Other%20scientists%20have%20shown%20that%20joyful%20experiences%20can%20influence%20plasticity%2C%20meaning%20the%20brain%20can%20increasingly%20adapt%20to%20new%20things%2C%20a%20critical%20human%20attribute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20human%20body%20has%20an%20estimated%2010-20%20billion%20neurons%20in%20the%20cerebral%20cortex%20and%2055-70%20billion%20neurons%20in%20the%20cerebellum%2C%20roughly%2076%20times%20that%20of%20the%20reptiles.%20A%20child's%20neural%20pathways%20are%20influenced%20in%20their%20development%20through%20exploration%2C%20thinking%2C%20problem-solving%20and%20language%20expressions%2C%20all%20of%20which%20are%20part%20of%20play%20episodes.%20In%20fact%2C%20games%20are%20considered%20to%20be%20so%20central%20to%20human%20development%20that%20it%20is%20formally%20recognised%20by%20the%20UN%20as%20a%20specific%20right%20for%20all%20children%2C%20under%20Article%2031.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Scourge%20Of%20Tuition%20Centres%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20education%20system%20is%20primarily%20driven%20by%20rote%20learning-driven%20exams%2C%20rather%20than%20by%20playful%20games.%20An%20Indian%20parent's%20self-esteem%20is%20often%20dictated%20by%20how%20well%20or%20badly%20their%20kids%20are%20doing%20in%20exams.%20Even%20today%2C%20as%20early%20as%20seven%20to%20eight%20years%20of%20age%20-%20an%20age%20when%20kids%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20developing%20their%20human%20potential%20with%20play%20-%20children%20are%20buried%20deep%20inside%20tuition%20centres%20around%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20ironic%20that%20early%20advancements%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%20have%20come%20from%20exploring%20and%20learning%20from%20games%2C%20like%20Chess%20and%20strategy%20games%20like%20Go.%20This%20was%20profiled%20in%20the%20documentary%20AlphaGo.%20At%20the%20%26quot%3BImprobably%20AI%20lab%26quot%3B%20at%20MIT%2C%20young%20researcher%20Pulkit%20Agrawal%20is%20exploring%20physical%20intelligence%20via%20robots%20that%20can%20learn%20and%20navigate%20complex%20natural%20terrains%20like%20steep%20hills%20on%20their%20own%20with%20algorithms%20leveraging%20playful%20curiosity.%20His%20lab's%20agile%20robots%20learning%20to%20kick%20the%20football%20are%20a%20fun%20sight%20and%20also%20signal%20how%20hard%20this%20simple%20step%20is%20for%20AI%20to%20master.%20Figure%20AI%20recently%20announced%20that%20their%20skilled%20humanoid%20robots%20will%20soon%20work%20on%20the%20BMW%20shop%20floor.%20Another%20startup%20called%20Skild%20AI%2C%20led%20by%20Deepak%20Pathak%2C%20recently%20raised%20%24300%20million%20to%20build%20robots%20that%20are%20learning%20to%20adapt%20to%20new%20environments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20Kids%20Play%20For%20The%20Future%20Of%20Work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Olympics%20are%20a%20great%20indicator%20of%20a%20society's%20progress%20in%20search%20of%20higher%20human%20potential.%20We%20should%20reflect%20on%20what%20we%20are%20training%20our%20kids'%20brains%20for%2C%20the%20past%20or%20the%20future.%20The%20upcoming%20Intelligence%20Economy%2C%20which%20is%20going%20to%20create%20a%20new%20economic%20value%20of%20%2415.7tn%20(PWC%20research)%20by%202030%2C%20is%20a%20great%20opportunity%20for%20India.%20The%20future%20of%20work%20is%20going%20to%20be%20creative%2C%20dynamic%2C%20complex%20and%20challenging.%20It%20will%20force%20us%20to%20learn%20new%20things%2C%20much%20like%20our%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20future%20value%20of%20our%20output%20will%20revolve%20around%20our%20core%20human%20potential%20to%20harness%20the%20state%20of%20%26quot%3Bflow%26quot%3B%20more%20often.%20India%20is%20the%20only%20country%20in%20the%20world%20with%20300%20million%20young%20human%20brains%2C%20with%20unexplored%20human%20potential%20and%20untapped%20intelligence.%20Bereft%20of%20exposure%20to%20the%20playground%2C%20can%20they%20really%20explore%20their%20unique%20physical%20and%20creative%20human%20potential%2C%20so%20critical%20for%20the%20upcoming%20opportunity%3F%20It%20is%20an%20important%20question%20to%20ask%20as%20they%20may%20eventually%20define%20the%20future%20of%20not%20just%20our%20nation%20but%20the%20future%20of%20the%20human%20race%20too%2C%20given%20the%20sheer%20strength%20in%20numbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020%20is%20a%20great%20start.%20However%2C%20the%20anxiety%20induced%20by%20parental%20pressure%2C%20portrayed%20poignantly%20in%20the%20web%20series%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kota%20Factory%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20harmful.%20ChatGPT%20has%20ensured%20that%20rather%20than%20knowing%20the%20answers%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20know%20what%20questions%20to%20ask.%20It's%20ironic%20that%20we%20are%20limiting%20our%20young%20human%20brains%20in%20these%20Kota-styled%20factories%20even%20as%20actual%20future%20factories%20are%20going%20to%20be%20manned%20by%20humanoid%20robots%20that%20are%20learning%20through%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20time%20to%20free%20our%20young%20minds%20to%20play%20and%20explore%20the%20world%20outside%20and%20within%2C%20as%20suggested%20by%20Rabindranath%20Tagore.%20This%20might%20result%20in%20more%20medals%20for%20us%20and%20enable%20India%20to%20excel%20in%20the%20AI-driven%20future%20of%20work.%20Can%20we%20resolve%20to%20hit%20the%20play%20button%20for%20our%20kids%20instead%20of%20the%20pause%20button%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BUmakant%20Soni%20is%20chairman%20of%20AIfoundry%2C%20co-founder%20of%20ARTPARK%20(AI%20%26amp%3B%20Robotics%20Technology%20Park)%2C%20and%20a%20passionate%20advocate%20for%20inclusive%20development%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1