fracture.%20The%20police%20have%20denied%20this%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%23FactCheck%202%3A%20'Unnatural%20Death'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20has%20said%20that%20the%20filing%20of%20an%20unnatural%20death%20case%20has%20raised%20suspicion%20and%20pulled%20up%20the%20hospital%20administration%20for%20not%20registering%20a%20complaint.%20As%20a%20matter%20of%20procedure%2C%20the%20police%20often%20register%20an%20unnatural%20death%20case%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20complaint.%20Unnatural%20death%20cases%20can%20turn%20into%20murder%20investigations%20upon%20receipt%20of%20a%20complaint%20or%20post-mortem%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnnatural%20death%20cases%20include%20suicide%2C%20murder%2C%20accident.%20The%20174%20of%20CrPC%20and%20the%20corresponding%20section%20of%20BNS%20explains%20this.%20This%20is%20simply%20a%20legal%20tool%20or%20procedure%20to%20begin%20probe%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Police%20chief%20Vineet%20Goyal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BUnnatural%20death%20case%20is%20a%20natural%20process.%20Murder%20is%20an%20unnatural%20death.%20When%20there%20is%20no%20immediate%20complaint%2C%20you%20have%20to%20do%20an%20inquest.%20An%20inquest%20is%20preceded%20by%20an%20unnatural%20death%20case.%20So%2C%20I%20don't%20see%20why%20it%20is%20being%20said%20that%20by%20registering%20an%20unnatural%20death%20case%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20hush%20up%20the%20matter%20and%20make%20it%20look%20like%20a%20suicide%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%23FactCheck%203%3A%20150%20mg%20Semen%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20reports%20that%20150%20mg%20of%20semen%20was%20found%20in%20the%20doctor's%20body%2C%20thereby%20suggesting%20gangrape.%20The%20source%20of%20this%20information%20was%20the%20petition%20filed%20by%20her%20family%20in%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court.%20The%20police%20chief%2C%20however%2C%20has%20denied%20this.%20In%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20Mr%20Goyal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSomeone%20said%20150%20gm%20semen%20is%20found.%20I%20don't%20know%20from%20where%20they%20have%20found%20this%20kind%20of%20Information.%20And%20it%20is%20circulating%20in%20media%20in%20all%20kinds%20of%20forms.%20People%20are%20tempted%20to%20believe%20it%20and%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20confusion%20among%20the%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%23FactCheck%204%3A%20Names%20Of%20Suspects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20social%20media%20posts%20have%20named%20some%20of%20the%20colleagues%20of%20the%20doctor%20as%20suspects.%20While%20sources%20say%20the%20parents%20have%20shared%20a%20list%20of%20names%20of%20the%20suspects%20with%20the%20CBI%2C%20no%20agency%20has%20named%20anyone%20on%20record%2C%20except%20the%20arrested%20civic%20volunteer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%23FactCheck%205%3A%20Son%20Of%20Powerful%20Politician%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20claimed%20on%20social%20media%20that%20one%20of%20doctor's%20junior%20colleague%20is%20the%20son%20of%20a%20powerful%20politician%20whereas%20he%20is%20son%20of%20a%20teacher%20from%20Bankura.%20The%20police%20say%20such%20fake%20narratives%20were%20propagated%20to%20claim%20some%20bigwigs%20are%20being%20protected%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20have%20also%20questioned%20how%20the%20doctor's%20name%20along%20with%20an%20unverified%20copy%20of%20a%20prescription%20written%20by%20her%20was%20leaked%20on%20social%20media%2C%20in%20direct%20violation%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20guidelines%20on%20reportage%20of%20sexual%20assault%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723874280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Foenr43e_doctors-strike_625x300_17_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkolkata-news%2Fkolkata-rg-kar-hospital-doctor-rape-murder-fractures-150-mg-semen-other-claims-denied-by-cops-in-kolkata-rape-murder-6356105%22%2C%22s