%20landed%20at%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%20on%20Saturday%2C%20August%2017%2C%20with%20thousands%20gathered%20outside%20to%20welcome%20her.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwrestling%2Fvinesh-phogat-receives-heros-welcome-from-fans-at-delhi-airport-breaks-down-watch-6356059%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IMF's%20Gita%20Gopinath%20Goes%20Bullish%20On%20India's%20Economic%20Growth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20during%20his%20Independence%20Day%20address%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20said%20the%20country%20is%20on%20its%20way%20to%20become%20the%20third-largest%20economy%20with%20big%20reforms%20across%20sectors%2C%20Gita%20Gopinath%2C%20Deputy%20Managing%20Director%20of%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%2C%20has%20stated%20that%20the%20country%20is%20likely%20to%20achieve%20this%20feat%20by%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20become%20the%20fifth-largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20is%20set%20to%20be%20among%20the%20top%20three%20global%20economic%20powers%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ms%20Gopinath%2C%20India's%20growth%20did%20much%20better%20than%20expected%20during%20the%20last%20fiscal%20year%20(FY24)%20as%20private%20consumption%20growth%20recovered%20across%20sectors%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20rural%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20two-wheeler%20sales%20to%20fast-moving%20consumer%20goods%20(FMCGs)%2C%20the%20overall%20consumption%20is%20surging.%20%26quot%3BWith%20better%20monsoons%20come%20better%20harvests%20and%20agricultural%20incomes%20go%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20in%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20latest%20data%20by%20the%20Society%20of%20Indian%20Automobile%20Manufacturers%20(SIAM)%2C%20the%20total%20production%20of%20passenger%20vehicles%2C%20three-wheelers%2C%20two-wheelers%20and%20quadricycle%20reached%2024%2C37%2C138%20units%20in%20July.%20Two-wheeler%20segment%20posted%20a%20decent%20growth%20of%2012.5%20per%20cent%20in%20July%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20month%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20FMCG%20market%20in%20India%20remains%20resilient%20despite%20challenges.%20According%20to%20marketing%20research%20firm%20Kantar%20Worldpanel%2C%20the%20FMCG%20sector%20is%20expected%20to%20register%206.1%20per%20cent%20yearly%20growth%20in%20FY%202024-25%20in%20the%20rural%20market%2C%20which%20was%204.4%20per%20cent%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20volumes%20in%20rural%20market%20could%20equal%20those%20in%20the%20urban%20market%2C%20which%20is%20higher%20at%20present.%20The%20rural%20FMCG%20market%20is%20more%20valuable%20to%20the%20industry%20than%20before%20and%20is%20generating%20almost%20half%20the%20volume%20and%20value%20for%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gopinath%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20country%20needs%20to%20create%20millions%20of%20additional%20jobs%20in%20the%20next%205-6%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMF%20has%20raised%20its%20economic%20growth%20forecast%20for%20the%20country%20for%20FY25%20to%207%20per%20cent%20from%206.8%20per%20cent%20projected%20in%20April.%20According%20to%20RBI%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%2C%20if%20the%20average%20growth%20India%20recorded%20over%20the%20three%20years%20is%20seen%2C%20the%20average%20comes%20to%208.3%20per%20cent.%20In%20the%20current%20year%2C%20they%20have%20given%20a%20projection%20of%207.2%20per%20cent%20growth.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723873920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fdjntjffo_imfs-gita-gopinath-calls-indias-g20-summit-successful-pm-modi-responds_62