erts%20have%20pointed%20to%20misalignment%20issues%20as%20a%20likely%20cause%20for%20these%20repeated%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20stone%20for%20the%203.16%20km%20bridge%20was%20laid%20on%20February%2023%2C%202014%2C%20with%20construction%20beginning%20on%20March%209%2C%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20government%20allocated%20Rs%201%2C710%20crore%20to%20the%20project%2C%20highlighting%20its%20significance%20as%20a%20major%20infrastructure%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20after%20nearly%20nine%20years%20in%20the%20making%2C%20the%20bridge%20remains%20incomplete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20government's%20road%20construction%20department%20has%20managed%20to%20build%20a%2016%20km%20approach%20road%20from%20the%20Khagaria%20side%20and%20a%204%20km%20approach%20road%20from%20the%20Bhagalpur%20side%2C%20but%20the%20main%20structure%20of%20the%20bridge%20remains%20unfinished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20long%20delay%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20repeated%20structural%20failures%2C%20has%20cast%20a%20shadow%20over%20the%20project's%20execution%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20work%20by%20SK%20Singla%20Construction%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20calls%20for%20an%20urgent%20review%20and%20corrective%20measures%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20bridge%2C%20once%20completed%2C%20is%20safe%20and%20reliable%20for%20public%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723871940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fe2p8b91o_bihar-bridge-collapse_625x300_17_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-under-construction-for-9-years-bridge-in-bihar-collapses-for-3rd-time-6355900%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bridge%20envisioned%20as%20a%20key%20infrastructure%20project%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20was%20intended%20to%20connect%20Sultanganj%20in%20Bhagalpur%20District%20with%20Aguani%20Ghat%20in%20Khagaria%20District.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engag