dtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdoctors-begin-24-hour-nationwide-strike-over-kolkata-rape-murder-10-points-6355326%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enationwide%20withdrawal%20of%20non-emergency%20health%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%2024%20hours%20beginning%20at%206%20am%2C%20over%20a%20week%20after%20the%20horrific%20incident%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkolkata-news%2Fparents-gave-names-of-interns-doctors-to-cbi-in-kolkata-horror-sources-6353432%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Kolkata.%20They%20also%20condemned%20the%20subsequent%20vandalism%20on%20the%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Patna%2C%20Bihar%3A%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%20announces%20nationwide%20strike%20over%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20rape%20%26amp%3B%20murder%20incident.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn(Visuals%20from%20Patna%20AIIMS)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FkmCr5pq0ZN%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FkmCr5pq0ZN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1824649540319973823%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20essential%20services%20will%20be%20maintained%20and%20casualties%20will%20be%20manned%2C%20the%20IMA%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20The%20routine%20OPDs%20will%20not%20function%20and%20elective%20surgeries%20will%20not%20be%20conducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20withdrawal%20is%20across%20all%20sectors%2C%20wherever%20modern%20medicine%20doctors%20are%20providing%20service%2C%20the%20top%20body%20of%20doctors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20RG%20Kar%20incident%20has%20brought%20to%20the%20fore%20two%20dimensions%20of%20violence%20in%20the%20hospital%3A%20A%20crime%20of%20barbaric%20scale%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20safe%20spaces%20for%20women%20and%20the%20hooliganism%20that%20is%20unleashed%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20an%20organised%20security%20protocol%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20crime%20and%20the%20vandalism%20have%20shocked%20the%20conscience%20of%20the%20nation.%20Today%2C%20both%20the%20medical%20fraternity%20and%20the%20nation%20are%20victims%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E5%20Demands%20Of%20Doctors%20On%20Nationwide%20Strike%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMA%20has%20put%20forth%20five%20demands%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20wants%20a%20significant%20policy%20to%20address%20violence%20against%20doctors%20and%20hospitals.%20The%20doctors'%20body%20is%20pushing%20for%20a%20Central%20Act%20that%20would%20incorporate%20the%20amendments%20made%20in%202023%20to%20the%20Epidemic%20Diseases%20Act%20of%201897%20into%20the%20proposed%20Hospital%20Protection%20Bill%20of%202019.%20This%20move%2C%20it%20said%2C%20would%20strengthen%20the%20existing%20legislation%20in%2025%20states.%20The%20IMA%20has%20suggested%20that%20an%20ordinance%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20enacted%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20would%20be%20appropriate%20in%20this%20situation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20IMA%20has%20also%20demanded%20that%20hospitals%20be%20declared%20safe%20zones%20with%20the%20first%20step%20being%20mandatory%20security%20entitlements.%20%26quot%3BThe%20security%20protocols%20of%20all%20hospitals%20should%20be%20no%20less%20than%20(that%20of)%20an%20airport.%20Declaring%20the%20hospitals%20as%20safe%20zones%20with%20mandatory%20security%20entitlements%20is%20the%20first%20step.%20CCTVs%2C%20deployment%20of%20security%20personnel%2C%20and%20the%20protocols%20can%20follow%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20IMA%20has%20demanded%20a%20thorough%20overhaul%20of%20the%20working%20and%20living%20conditions%20of%20resident%20doctors%2C%20including%20the%2036-hour%20duty%20shift%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20in%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20safe%20spaces%20to%20take%20a%20rest.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20IMA%20has%20also%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bmeticulous%20and%20professional%26quot%3B%20investigation%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20horror%20in%20a%20specific%20time%20frame%20and%20rendering%20of%20justice%20besides%20identifying%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20vandalism%20of%20the%20hospital%20premises%20and%20awarding%20exemplary%20punishment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20doctors'%20body%20has%20also%20sought%20an%20appropriate%20and%20dignified%20compensation%20to%20the%20bereaved%20family%20commensurate%20with%20the%20cruelty%20inflicted.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trainee%20doctor%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20last%20week%20inside%20a%20medical%20college%20in%20Kolkata%20where%20she%20worked%2C%20triggering%20nationwide%20protests%20among%20doctors.%20Anger%20at%20the%20failure%20of%20tough%20laws%20to%20deter%20a%20rising%20tide%20of%20violence%20against%20women%20has%20fuelled%20widespread%20protests%20by%20doctors%20and%20women's%20groups%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723868160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fej1qdqlo_kolkata-doctors-_625x300_17_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-rape-murder-case-5-demands-of-doctors-on-24-hour-nationwide-strike-6355587%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Doctors%20have%20begun%20their%2024-hour%20nationwide%20strike%20today%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20trainee%20doctor%20in%20Kolkata.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-rape-murder-case-5-demands-of-doctor