a%20priority%2C%20according%20to%20Christopher%20Mayer%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20real%20estate%20at%20Columbia%20Business%20School%20who%20praised%20Harris'%20emphasis%20on%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20most%20people%20should%20be%20homeowners%2C%26quot%3B%20Mayer%20said%2C%20noting%20the%20falling%20homeownership%20rate%20among%20young%20people.%20%26quot%3BOwning%20a%20home%20is%20a%20proven%20way%20of%20building%20wealth.%20It%20creates%20stability%20for%20households.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223131%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rows%20of%20identical%20homes%20with%20uniform%20driveways%20and%20streets%20stretch%20towards%20the%20desert%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6697bf635439fb59cebe092a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222348%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Las%20Vegas%20housing%20development%20similar%20to%20Tao's%20property.%3Cp%3EJames%20Marshall%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e83522f-24d6-4242-ba18-9043bcae7584%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAddressing%20the%20housing%20shortage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20the%20low%20supply%20of%20starter%20homes%2C%20those%20making%20the%20jump%20from%20renting%20to%20owning%20often%20have%20to%20contend%20with%20both%20high%20prices%20and%20steep%20mortgage%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerica%20is%20facing%20a%20significant%20housing%20shortage%2C%20with%20the%20country%20between%204%20and%207%20million%20homes%20short%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2024%2F04%2F23%2F1246623204%2Fhousing-experts-say-there-just-arent-enough-homes-in-the-u-s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENPR%20reported%20in%20the%20spring%20of%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Builders%20have%20cited%20supply%20chain%20issues%2C%20among%20other%20reasons%20building%20has%20stalled.%20Zoning%20also%20remains%20a%20large%20barrier%20to%20homes%20being%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECOVID-19%20on