et%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Parking%20Spot%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20buy%20tickets%20for%20Pilgrimage%20Music%20Festival%202024%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20this%20writing%2C%20the%20Pilgrimage%20Music%20Festival%20still%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpilgrimagefestival.com%2Ftickets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20original%20tickets%20remaining.%3C%2Fa%3E%20However%2C%20with%20previous%20years%20selling%20out%2C%20the%202024%20event%20will%20likely%20see%20similar%20success%20as%20it%20nears.%20Kids%20aged%207%20and%20under%20are%20admitted%20free%20with%20a%20paid%20adult%2C%20though%20VIP%20areas%20require%20a%20VIP%20ticket%20above%20age%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20original%20tickets%20remain%2C%20verified%20third-party%20resellers%20may%20offer%20options%20at%20similar%20or%20even%20lower%20prices.%20StubHub%20and%20Vivid%20Seats%20both%20list%20a%20variety%20of%20ticket%20options%20available%2C%20including%20general%20admission%20and%20VIP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20outdoor%20music%20festival%2C%20the%20event%20doesn't%20have%20assigned%20seating%20outside%20of%20viewing%20areas%20that%20are%20exclusive%20to%20VIP%20ticket%20holders.%20The%20stages%20include%20both%20a%20standing-room-only%20area%20and%20areas%20where%20fans%20are%20allowed%20to%20bring%20low-backed%20chairs%20(under%2030%20inches)%20and%20blankets%20to%20sit%20back%20and%20watch%20the%20performances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20music%20tends%20to%20drive%20ticket%20sales%2C%20the%20festival%20experience%20goes%20beyond%20the%20three%20stages.%20The%20Americana%20Music%20Triangle%20area%20is%20a%20celebration%20of%20the%20history%20of%20southern%20music.%20The%20Franklin%20Fun%20Farm%20area%20features%20events%20and%20activities%20for%20families%20and%20kids%2C%20including%20youth%20bands%2C%20aerialists%2C%20magic%20shows%2C%20games%2C%20and%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20are%20Pilgrimage%20Music%20Festival%20tickets%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pilgrimage%20Music%20Festival%20uses%20a%20tier%20system%2C%20which%20means%20the%20earlier%20you%20buy%20tickets%2C%20the%20lower%20the%20cost.%20With%20the%20festival%20only%20about%20six%20weeks%20away%2C%20the%20only%20original%20tickets%20remaining%20are%20in%20the%20top%20third%20tier.%20Fans%20who%20enjoy%20the%20festival%20this%20year%20and%20want%20to%20return%20may%20want%20to%20plan%20ahead%20and%20purchase%202025%20tickets%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20tier%20original%20tickets%20that%20remain%20sell%20for%20about%20%24290%20for%20a%20two-day%20pass%20or%20%24180%20for%20a%20single-day%20pass%2C%20plus%20fees%20for%20general%20admission.%20The%20festival's%20policies%20prohibit%20reselling%20tickets%20at%20a%20cost%20higher%20than%20the%20original%20face%20value%2C%20which%20means%20general%20admission%20tickets%20from%20verified%20third-party%20resellers%20like%20StubHub%20and%20Vivid%20Seats%20sit%20at%20a%20similar%20or%20sometimes%20lower%20price%20point.%20For%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Df19592ec9d073eae16467e5799a6438e8abc85b74d0d8ee565bc4f3bfa4d9ec6%26postID%3D66bfa73d7d61a86c186b65d4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftickets%252Fhow-to-buy-pilgrimage-music-festival-tickets%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.stubhub.com%252Fpilgrimage-music-and-cultural-festival-tickets%252Fgrouping%252F1503160%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStubHub%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20two-day%20pass%20listed%20for%20about%20%2475%20less%20than%20the%20original%20cost%2C%20though%20that%20does%20not%20include%20fees%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dc76f625d2a4973eed590fd4e50ea4306a7dae565d95f64128352d0ce80a33f01%26postID%3D66bfa73d7d61a86c186b65d4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftickets%252Fhow-to-buy-pilgrimage-music-festi