.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fvladimir-putin-ally-alexander-lukashenko-urges-russia-and-ukraine-to-end-war-13197650%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fvladimir-putin-ally-alexander-lukashenko-urges-russia-and-ukraine-to-end-war-13197650%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kanyakumari%20to%20Ladakh%20on%20a%20Bike%3A%2017-YO%20Shares%20Lessons%20From%20a%207000%20Km%20Road%20Trip%20With%20Her%20Dad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Angelica%20Daniel%2C%20then%2014%2C%20was%20preparing%20for%20the%20prelims%20of%20her%20Class%2010%20Board%20exams%2C%20when%20her%20father%20Ajay%20Daniel%20(46)%20suggested%20%E2%80%9Csomething%20crazy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJoin%20me%20on%20a%20road%20trip%20to%20Khardung%20La.%E2%80%9D%20The%20ask%20was%20a%20last-minute%20one%2C%20Ajay%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20been%20planning%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F135467%2Ftwo-women-shubra-acharya-amrutha-kashinath-kanyakumari-leh-motorcycle-expedition-record-time%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20motorbike%20ride%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20few%20friends%20from%20Chandigarh%20to%20the%20Khardung%20La%20pass%20(one%20of%20the%20highest%20motorable%20roads%20in%20the%20world)%20in%20Leh.%20My%20bike%20had%20been%20shipped%20to%20Chandigarh%20and%20my%20flight%20tickets%20were%20booked.%20A%20week%20before%20setting%20off%2C%20everyone%20backed%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWatching%20her%20father%20disappointed%20at%20the%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20that%20was%20now%20threatened%20to%20flop%20%E2%80%94%20Angelica%20said%20a%20%E2%80%98yes%E2%80%99%20when%20asked%20if%20she%20would%20oblige%20to%20be%20his%20travel%20buddy.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20every%20day%20that%20someone%20gets%20to%20share%20in%20something%20like%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20in%20retrospect.%20The%20trip%20was%20phenomenal%20and%20the%20duo%20made%20it%20back%20just%20in%20time%20for%20her