0of%20land%20that%20was%20completely%20deserted%20without%20a%20trace%20of%20civilisation.%20It%20was%20an%20eerie%20sight.%E2%80%9D%20While%20riding%20through%20this%20dystopian%20landscape%2C%20the%20duo%20felt%20snow%20falling%20steadily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20weren%E2%80%99t%20wearing%20warm%20clothes%2C%20had%20lost%20signal%20and%20so%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20access%20maps.%20It%20was%20beginning%20to%20get%20dark%20and%20we%20were%20scared%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20While%20Ajay%20continued%20riding%20undeterred%2C%20his%2017-year-old%20pillion%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20as%20calm.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20roads%20in%20Ladakh%20are%20incredibly%20narrow.%20If%20the%20bike%20skid%20even%20a%20little%2C%20we%E2%80%99d%20be%20thrown%20off%20the%20mountain.%E2%80%9D%20But%20it%20was%20during%20these%20%E2%80%9Cfreakish%E2%80%9D%20moments%20that%20Ajay%20encouraged%20Angelica%20to%20calm%20her%20mind%20by%20singing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Let%20It%20Go%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20Disney%20movie%20%E2%80%98Frozen%E2%80%99%20was%20the%20song%20of%20choice.%20%E2%80%9CEventually%20we%20saw%20a%20milestone%20indicating%20a%20village%20nearby%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20sighs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20memories%20on%20the%20road%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20trip%20from%20Chandigarh%20to%20Khardung%20La%20in%202021%2C%20the%20duo%20drove%20from%20Chandigarh%20to%20Umling%20La%20(said%20to%20be%20the%20highest%20motorable%20road%20and%20one%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20passes%20in%20the%20world)%20in%202022%2C%20followed%20by%20the%207%2C000%20km%20ride%20in%202023.%20The%20third%20ride%20made%20Angelica%20the%20youngest%20pillion%20rider%20to%20complete%20such%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F138055%2Fdilip-pooja-chauhan-ujjain-bike-road-trip%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emotorcycle%20expedition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20the%20India%20Book%