%2C%20planters%2C%20and%20other%20eco-friendly%20gift%20items.%20Employing%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvalue-based%20recycling%20technology%E2%80%9D%20to%20manufacture%20them%2C%20%3Cem%3Eeconscious%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20sought%20to%20walk%20the%20talk%20on%20creating%20a%20circular%20economy%20around%20plastic%20waste%20and%20driving%20greater%20awareness%20for%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20business%20during%20COVID-19%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20early%20months%20of%20%3Cem%3Eeconscious%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewere%20both%20challenging%20and%20exciting.%20With%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20still%20affecting%20daily%20life%2C%20we%20had%20to%20navigate%20restrictions%20while%20developing%20our%20initial%20products.%20We%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20researching%20and%20prototyping%2C%20trying%20to%20find%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289275%2Fhyderabad-startup-banyan-nation-recycles-plastic-waste-into-fmcg-product-bottles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecycle%20plastic%20waste%20into%20useful%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sonal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20first%20project%20involved%20creating%20an%20eco-board%20out%20of%20plastic%20waste.%20This%20board%20was%20a%20prototype%20and%20could%20be%20used%20for%20multiple%20applications.%20This%20project%20was%20significant%20as%20it%20allowed%20us%20to%20demonstrate%20the%20practical%20application%20of%20our%20recycling%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20worked%20on%20creating%20eco-friendly%20gifting%20items%2C%20such%20as%20planters%20and%20coasters%2C%20which%20helped%20them%20reach%20a%20wider%20audience%20and%20spread%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20recycling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20after%20much%20experimentation%2C%20we%20found%20that%20products%20that%20can%20be%20used%20in%20public%20