ay-rishikesh-raghav-ansh-kumar-delhi-architects-cob-sustainable-home%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealways%20knew%20they%20wanted%20to%20settle%20in%20the%20hills%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20they%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20that%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuite%20surprisingly%2C%20their%20caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99s%20USP%20was%20its%20continental%20food.%20Amit%20and%20Shipra%20taught%20their%20staff%20how%20to%20cook%20pizzas%2C%20pastas%2C%20and%20make%20milkshakes.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20allure%20of%20having%20continental%20dishes%20in%20a%20village%20was%20fascinating%20to%20both%20locals%20and%20visitors%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20soared%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20flood%20of%20customers%20and%20a%20stream%20of%20positive%20reviews%20online.%20The%20scenic%20countryside%20view%20made%20waiting%20in%20line%20a%20pleasant%20experience%20for%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%202017%2C%20the%20couple%20relocated%20their%20caf%C3%A9%20to%20Lansdowne.%20The%20reason%3F%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20a%20remote%2C%20less%20commercialised%20location%20to%20create%20a%20truly%20unique%20experience%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shipra%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELansdowne%E2%80%99s%20dense%20forests%20were%20perfect%20for%20them%20%E2%80%94%20they%20wanted%20to%20be%20close%20to%20nature%20and%20enjoy%20mountain%20treks.%20The%20area%E2%80%99s%20quiet%20charm%20and%20its%20closeness%20to%20their%20old%20place%20in%20Devikhal%20were%20also%20big%20pluses.%20Besides%2C%20they%20were%20confident%20that%20their%20loyal%20customers%20would%20make%20the%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201156px)%20100vw%2C%201156px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.24_11zon-1723126958.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221156%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22They%20knew%20t